                <p>Where this is a joint tenancy, the term “Tenant” applies to each of the individuals above and the full responsibilities and rights set out in this Agreement apply to each Tenant who will be jointly and severally liable for all of the obligations of the Tenant under this Agreement. </p>

                <p>Email address(es):</p>

                <ol>
                {{#each tenants}}
                    <li><span class="summary__user-input">{{{notspecified email}}}</span></li>
                {{/each}}
                </ol>

                <p>Telephone number(s)</p>

                <ol>
                {{#each tenants}}
                    <li><span class="summary__user-input">{{{notspecified telephone}}}</span></li>
                {{/each}}
                </ol>

            {{else}}

                <p>No tenants specified.</p>

            {{/if}}
        </div>
    </div>

    {{#compare hasLettingAgent 'letting-agent-yes'}}
