            <span class="summary__user-input">
                {{{notspecified propertyAddress}}}
            </span><br>
            (“the Let Property”)</p>

            <p>Type of property: <span class="summary__user-input">{{{notspecified propertyType_text}}}
            {{#compare propertyType 'OTHER'}}
                {{#if buildingOther}}
                    ({{{notspecified buildingOther}}})
                {{/if}}
            {{/compare}}</span></p>

            <p>Any other areas/facilities included with the Let Property:</p>
            <ul class="blank-if-empty"><!--
                -->{{#each facilities}}<!--
                    -->{{#compare type 'INCLUDED'}}<!--
                        --><li><span class="summary__user-input">{{name}}</span></li><!--
                    -->{{/compare}}<!--
                -->{{/each}}<!--
            --></ul>

            <p>Any shared areas/facilities:</p>
            <ul class="blank-if-empty"><!--
                -->{{#each facilities}}<!--
                -->{{#compare type 'SHARED'}}<!--
                        --><li><span class="summary__user-input">{{name}}</span></li><!--
                    -->{{/compare}}<!--
                -->{{/each}}<!--
            --></ul>

            <p>Any excluded areas/facilities:</p>
            <ul class="blank-if-empty"><!--
                -->{{#each facilities}}<!--
                -->{{#compare type 'EXCLUDED'}}<!--
                        --><li><span class="summary__user-input">{{name}}</span></li><!--
                    -->{{/compare}}<!--
                -->{{/each}}<!--
            --></ul>

            <p>The Let Property is <span class="summary__user-input" style="text-transform: lowercase;">{{{notspecified furnishingType_text}}}</span>.  See the Inventory and Record of Condition for further details.</p>

            <p>The Let Property <span class="summary__user-input">{{#compare inRentPressureZone true}}is{{/compare}}{{#compare inRentPressureZone false}}is not{{/compare}}{{#compare inRentPressureZone null}}[is not/is]{{/compare}}</span> located in a rent pressure zone. </p>

            <p>If Scottish Ministers have designated the area that the Let Property is located in as a rent pressure zone, there will be a cap on the amount that the rent can be increased.  You can check whether the Let Property shown above is located in a rent pressure zone on the Scottish Government’s website <a href="https://www.mygov.scot/rent-pressure-zone-checker/" target="_blank">https://www.mygov.scot/rent-pressure-zone-checker/ (opens in a new window)</a>.</p>

            <p>The Let Property <span class="summary__user-input">{{#compare hmoProperty 'true'}}is{{/compare}}{{#compare hmoProperty 'false'}}is not{{/compare}}{{#compare hmoProperty null}}[is not/is]{{/compare}}</span> a House in Multiple Occupation (HMO).</p>

