            {{/compare}}
            {{#compare hmoProperty null}}
            <p>HMO 24-hour contact number: <span class="summary__user-input">{{{notspecified hmo24ContactNumber}}}</span></p>

            <p>HMO licence expiry date: <span class="summary__user-input">{{{notspecified hmoRegistrationExpiryDate}}}</span></p>
