    <div class="ds_accordion-item">
        <input type="checkbox" class="visually-hidden  ds_accordion-item__control" id="panel-rent" aria-labelledby="panel-rent-heading" />
        <div class="ds_accordion-item__header">
            <h3 id="panel-rent-heading" class="ds_accordion-item__title">
                Rent
            </h3>
            <span class="ds_accordion-item__indicator"></span>
            <label class="ds_accordion-item__label" for="panel-rent"><span class="visually-hidden">Show this section</span></label>
        </div>

        <div class="ds_accordion-item__body" id="accordion-item-rent">
            <p>The rent is £<span class="summary__user-input">{{{notspecified rentAmount}}}
            {{#compare rentPaymentFrequency 'WEEKLY'}}a week{{/compare}}
            {{#compare rentPaymentFrequency 'FORTNIGHTLY'}}a fortnight{{/compare}}
            {{#compare rentPaymentFrequency 'EVERY_FOUR_WEEKS'}}every four weeks{{/compare}}
            {{#compare rentPaymentFrequency 'CALENDAR_MONTH'}}a calendar month{{/compare}}
            {{#compare rentPaymentFrequency 'QUARTERLY'}}a quarter{{/compare}}
            {{#compare rentPaymentFrequency 'EVERY_SIX_MONTHS'}}every six months{{/compare}}
            {{#compare rentPaymentFrequency ''}}<span class="summary__blank" title="not specified"></span>{{/compare}}
            </span>
             payable in <span class="summary__user-input blank-if-empty" style="text-transform: lowercase;">{{#compare rentPayableInAdvance "true"}}advance{{/compare}}{{#compare rentPayableInAdvance "false"}}arrears{{/compare}}</span>.</p>

            <p>The first payment will be paid on <span class="summary__user-input">{{{notspecified firstPaymentDate}}}</span> and will be for the sum of £<span class="summary__user-input">{{{notspecified firstPaymentAmount}}}</span> in respect of the period <span class="summary__user-input">{{{notspecified tenancyStartDate}}}</span> to <span class="summary__user-input">{{{notspecified firstPaymentPeriodEnd}}}</span>. (The maximum amount of rent which can be paid in advance is 6 months' rent).</p>

            <p>Thereafter payments of £<span class="summary__user-input" style="text-transform: lowercase;">{{{notspecified rentAmount}}}</span> must be received on <span class="summary__user-input">
            {{#compare rentPaymentFrequency 'WEEKLY'}}{{{notspecified rentPaymentScheduleObject.day}}}{{/compare}}
            {{#compare rentPaymentFrequency 'FORTNIGHTLY'}}{{{notspecified rentPaymentScheduleObject.day}}} of the <span style="text-transform: lowercase;">{{{notspecified rentPaymentScheduleObject.week}}}</span>{{/compare}}
            {{#compare rentPaymentFrequency 'EVERY_FOUR_WEEKS'}}{{{notspecified rentPaymentScheduleObject.day}}} of the <span style="text-transform: lowercase;">{{{notspecified rentPaymentScheduleObject.week}}}</span>{{/compare}}
            {{#compare rentPaymentFrequency 'CALENDAR_MONTH'}}the {{{notspecified rentPaymentScheduleObject.date}}} of the month{{/compare}}
            {{#compare rentPaymentFrequency 'QUARTERLY'}} the {{{notspecified rentPaymentScheduleObject.date}}}{{/compare}}
            {{#compare rentPaymentFrequency 'EVERY_SIX_MONTHS'}} the {{{notspecified rentPaymentScheduleObject.date}}}{{/compare}}
            {{#compare rentPaymentFrequency ''}}<span class="summary__blank" title="not specified"></span>{{/compare}}</span>
             and then subsequently on or before the same <span class="summary__user-input blank-if-empty"><!--
            -->{{#compare rentPaymentFrequency 'WEEKLY'}}day of each week{{/compare}}<!--
            -->{{#compare rentPaymentFrequency 'FORTNIGHTLY'}}day of each fortnight{{/compare}}<!--
            -->{{#compare rentPaymentFrequency 'EVERY_FOUR_WEEKS'}}day of each four weekly period{{/compare}}<!--
            -->{{#compare rentPaymentFrequency 'CALENDAR_MONTH'}}date each calendar month{{/compare}}<!--
            -->{{#compare rentPaymentFrequency 'QUARTERLY'}}date each quarter{{/compare}}<!--
            -->{{#compare rentPaymentFrequency 'EVERY_SIX_MONTHS'}}date each 6-month period{{/compare}}<!--
            --></span> thereafter. </p>

            <p>Method by which rent is to be paid: <span class="summary__user-input">{{{notspecified rentPaymentMethod_text}}}</span> <br>
            (This is the preferred method but rent may be paid using another method if it is reasonable in the circumstances.)</p>

            <p>The following services are included in the rent amount noted above:</p>
            <ul class="blank-if-empty"><!--
            -->{{#each servicesIncludedInRent}}<!--
                    --><li class="hide-if-empty"><span class="summary__user-input">{{name}}{{#if name}} - {{/if}}£{{value}}</span></li><!--
